common_issues.title: Multiple PiecesOS Installations Detected
common_issues.description: Multiple PiecesOS installations detected on Windows 10 machines, causing installation failures.  Users should uninstall all but one PiecesOS installation via 'Add or Remove Programs' to resolve the issue. The error message suggests potential data corruption or unexpected errors if multiple installations exist.

recommendations: Prioritize resolving the 'Multiple PiecesOS Installations Detected' issue by providing clear instructions to users on how to uninstall duplicate installations.
Investigate the root cause of multiple PiecesOS installations occurring on Windows 10 machines.
Improve the installation process to prevent multiple installations or provide automatic detection and resolution during installation.
Monitor the frequency of this issue to track the effectiveness of implemented solutions.
